/*

bmc								: Case-Control variable, Case=1 and Controls=0
Excl_arecanut_YN				: Exclusive areca nut users, non-smokers, non-chewers of tobacco, and non-drinkers of alcohol, Ever-user=1 and Never-user=0
Age								: The age of participant at the time of enrolment, continuous variable, Min=19 and Max=71  
Gender							: Sex of the participant, Male=1 and Female=0
edu_5yrs_foradj					: Education categories of the participant, <=5 years=1 and >5 years=0
Cur_res_Zone_foradj				: Indian zone of residence at the time of enrolment, Central=1, East=2, North=4, South=5, West=6
bmi_cat_india					: BMI categories, Normal[18.5-24.9]=1, Obese[>30.0]=2, Overweight[24.9-30.0]=3, Severely-underweight[<16.5]=4 , Underweight[16.5-18.5]=5
Any_areca_dur_cat				: Duration in years areca nut was consumed by the participant during their lifetime, Categorised as Never-users=0, <=15 years=1, and >15 years=2; 15 is the median year of consumption among the controls
Any_areca_age_at_start_medcat	: Age of the participant at when areca nut consumption began, Categorised as Never-user=0, <=25 years=1, and >25 years=2; 25 is the median age of start among the controls

*/

